{"tid":655460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家正研發家用主動降噪裝置，如果可以將外來的噪音減少，擁有一個寧靜的家，相信是很多香港人的夢想。","createTime":"2018-05-06T13:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T15:22:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"536c40ba23a50fe79de0c8b9e8f247e439aa629f","tid":655460,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"香港幾乎是一個 24 小時不停止的城市，就算在深宵時分，外面都可能傳來各種噪音，更遑論是其他時間。外面的車聲人聲，或者就近地盤或修路的工程聲音，都有可能影響工作、溫習或休息，如果可以將外來的噪音減少，擁有一個寧靜的家，相信是很多香港人的夢想。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/0506-2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F0506-2a.jpg&h=45b50c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近新加坡南洋理工大學有研究人員就開發了可以安裝在窗戶，就能夠有效減少外來噪音的裝置。這個噪音消除裝置的工作原理並非將聲音阻擋，而是利用自己的聲波去主動對抗，透過利用咪高峰去監聽從外面傳入的噪音，然後利用演算法對聲音波形進行分析，在製造反向版本的聲波。就算打開窗都可以享受相對寧靜的空間，研究團隊認為這樣可以減少使用冷氣，慳電費之餘亦更加環保。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/06/open-window-noise-cancellation-technology/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2Fopen-window-noise-cancellation-technology%2Flife-tech%2F&d=yrWxp8spTKOudE0FY6n35b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8001eb36\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/06/open-window-noise-cancellation-technology/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"c859d217075d5a1854864244ec7f5f162bea1dca","tid":655460,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/0506-2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F0506-2b.jpg&h=cb3a0bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當兩組聲音匯合的時候，外來的噪音就會被抵銷降低，房間內的人就不會聽到外面的噪音。其實類似的主動降噪技術，一早已經被應用於耳機、耳塞、電單車安全頭盔、汽車車廂和防打鼻鼾的裝置，不過南洋理工大學的團隊將自應用到家居窗戶。團隊負責人 Gan Woon Seng 指項目創新之處在不但需要計算噪音的類型和數量，而且要比噪音到達裝置內部更快。<br />\n<br />\n來源：innovationtoronto"},{"pid":"9806f9aa859f54afccc67253b4e636ec2c737e2b","tid":655460,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"降噪耳機喇叭版"},{"pid":"ab7fe488d387b22536d486272d09106b3230425c","tid":655460,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"叫耳塞"},{"pid":"637f19bf137af02a5469007bd137cd9d2976ffd3","tid":655460,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"destructively interference of waveforms"},{"pid":"d673d6ce674bd45455be0e160dd79de2cbaaa5c4","tid":655460,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"低頻嘅噪音先係最恐怖"},{"pid":"371ca5ccae6890b5a77f58b38fe931096a9c7756","tid":655460,"uid":91721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"諗起一個kickstarter 騙局，又係講呢樣"},{"pid":"c6890bcd73b04457f58a38180cc4ea985d3d6500","tid":655460,"uid":34461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"咁高要求嘅，我淨係想有瓦遮頭"},{"pid":"73d4d1548e978259b1e94efcda4e267a0b029ca4","tid":655460,"uid":86960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"371ca5ccae6890b5a77f58b38fe931096a9c7756","tid":655460,"uid":91721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"諗起一個kickstarter 騙局，又係講呢樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"果個真係仆街黎"},{"pid":"cf68a147128d5a417ba74f956e67cdcde33b3a12","tid":655460,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:02:03.000Z","msg":"唔明點解可以測到噪音後即刻發出同一粒音去抵消，點解快到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10eb407cd623d3a06ca810331b1cebf0b32e7289","tid":655460,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"有都極貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ed31674b817d537a1ee313a5210d3473369094","tid":655460,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf68a147128d5a417ba74f956e67cdcde33b3a12","tid":655460,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:02:03.000Z","msg":"唔明點解可以測到噪音後即刻發出同一粒音去抵消，點解快到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"聲波波段抵消"},{"pid":"a85d47e4271845b6b1e5c7c19342f1fcb53ae6cb","tid":655460,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:04:58.000Z","msg":"理工又贏"},{"pid":"9b76d6f2673d529e9a1af9d687f247e7f7b67d59","tid":655460,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"創科局又投資左去邊樹？"}]}